Fix out-of-memory error in Firebear's Search Terms importer. Its constructor preloads the whole
search_query table into memory, which triggers an OOM on opening, validating, and running the import.
This patch skips that preload and resolves existing query ids on demand instead.
Ticket: IPET-2806

